rainbow table attack : 
huge precomputed list of password - hash 
eg: 
123456  → e10adc3949ba59abbe56e057f20f883e
password → 5f4dcc3b5aa765d61d8327deb882cf99
admin    → 21232f297a57a5a743894a0e4a801fc3

Rainbow tables exploit unsalted, fast hashes


Collision Attacks(shattered attack)|
- Different inputs -> same hash 
file1 → hash123
file2 → hash123   ← different file, same hash 
If hashes are used for:File verification, Digital signatures, Security checks
